data.title: Shabby, Chic and more antiques
data.text:
Wandered in here and discovered a montage of old farm, american craft women's jewelery, antique items, some furniture, all tastefully displayed by about 20 vendors
in tasteful and clean settings with easy access to most items....Some local
home decor items locally made (USA OK)--- This enterprise/shop is owned by 
Karen Nitkey... She is also a buyer....restroom for patrons only---this store is worth
time to browse and enjoy. It smells really nice in there.
